Author: Enkh D#1827
Content: Is there anyway to see orderbook on atomicdex? or am i just able to see my orders?

Author: gcharang#6833
Content:
@Enkh D you can see orders for the coins you have  a balance for right now in atomicDEX
but seeing the whole orderbook is possible and in the expected feature list
in the meantime, you can see the orderbook here with a  15 minute delay
<https://www.oracle.earth/mm2_orderbook/>
